channel.title: Very Funny Videos I found on Google
channel.description:
I googled Underoath because Yahoo hates Opera. I came up with some "interesting" results. It's kids lipsyncing underoath, and they do a damned funny job of it. Hysterical to Underoath lovers, but still funny for others.
Recommended if you need a good laugh.
5 Girls all with "instruments" http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4797763852192095865&q=underoath
Some guy who bounces around his room http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=987598327836386735&q=underoath
Stereotypical "emo" kids trying to "hXc" dance. Freaking great lmfao. http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-3238343808089291324&q=underoath
Some chick in her car acting out the song http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-6815198432863531186&q=underoath
This guy actually screams the song http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=2282658915499745099&q=underoath
More "hXc" dancing http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-8509732528296460356&q=underoath
Some odd kids doing lipsynchs of a few songs http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=1074223948956236546&q=underoath
